<br>
For example, Bryan and Rey are two drivers from another group called the Spartans. Scott is tempted to join them becaus ethey share his view of driving and tuning, but are a bit too aggressive for his liking. That's a bit of a subplot.<br>
<br>
I also explain later on how Scott's father got him started racing go karts at the age of 8. Even after Scott's father died in an accident, Scott kept practicing, and now he's an excellent driver.<br>
<br>
Scott is actually a bit of a generic guy. He isn't Asian, either.lol One thing that makes him stand out is how timid he is, especially when it comes to driving. He is very good, but tends to hold back quite a bit. This gets him into trouble every now and then. Something of a tragic flaw, see?<br>
